content: Singaporean entrepreneur (born 1985) **Rachel Kum** (born 8 April 1985) is a [Singaporean](/wiki/Singaporean) entrepreneur, model and beauty pageant titleholder. She co-founded the Singaporean company Rachel K Cosmetics. She won [Miss Singapore Universe](/wiki/Miss_Singapore_Universe) 2009 and represented Singapore in the [Miss Universe 2009](/wiki/Miss_Universe_2009) pageant which was held at the [Atlantis Paradise Island](/wiki/Atlantis_Paradise_Island) in [Nassau](/wiki/Nassau,_Bahamas), Bahamas on 23 August 2009. ## Career Born and raised in Singapore, Kum graduated from Finance at the [University of Western Australia](/wiki/University_of_Western_Australia). She created her own cosmetic brand, Rachel K Cosmetics. In 2009, Kum was featured in a [Windows](/wiki/Microsoft_Windows) commercial on [AXN Asia](/wiki/AXN_Asia) television. - Rachel K Cosmetics - Miss Universe
title: Rachel Kum
